reviews.review_text: We were looking for goldfish and there were good variety of them.

Our 1st grooming for our puppy was at Pet Smart and we couldn t have picked a better place!  We had originally booked somewhere else but they refused our puppy as she was a little matted but the groomer at Pet Smart took our puppy and did an excellent job!  Josie was patient, kind, professional and answered all of our questions. She took such great care of our puppy and I could tell our puppy was in great hands as she seemed calm when Josie held her. Thank you for making our 1st grooming experience an awesome one! We will definitely be back!!!
Awesome staff. Very welcoming and accommodating

Staff is super friendly and helpful.  I went to this location and purchased tetra glofish, a 10 gallon tank and some accessories, fish food, cleaning supplies ect.  They were so willing to answer any questions I had and didnt try to over sell me anything.  Definitely recommend this location solely based on their staff.

I visited this store for the first time yesterday and was very impressed.  The selection of food, treats and toys for my beloved lab is amazing.  I love the interior store layout--it doesn t feel like a traditional big box store. It feels more cozy, almost like an independent, locally-owned neighborhood shop.  The store associates with whom I interacted were friendly, helpful, knowledgeable, and quick.  This location is next to a lot of other stores that I already shop at, so it s super convenient too.  This is West Vancouver s new premier destination for all of your pet supply needs.  Bravo PetSmart!
I love this petsmart!! Sometimes they don t have certain items or they re out of stock but the staff are also so friendly!! It makes the experience fantastic.

Great customer service! Also take my pup here for training classes and we ve learned a lot. Appreciate the patience and kindness of staff when my puppy is a bit over threshold. She loves coming in and getting some treats!

Had a really really great experience with Alex. This superhuman helped us understand how to handle hamsters with confidence and he showed genuine interest and care in my familys experience with a pet and helped ensure that our pets experience would be good as well.  Cant thank Alex enough.
